{"tid":836861,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中共藉腰斬《人民公敵》滅聲","createTime":"2018-09-26T03:13:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-26T06:10:25.000Z","uid":25558,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"1d4d14e8cad725023945cedad907f6f2ac8b9f16","tid":836861,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T03:13:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180926/20508084\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180926%2F20508084&d=u3SIyLTQir9PnOjdAi7mCr%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=1825fd5f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180926%2F20508084&h=402f9538\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180926/20508084</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年09月26日 <br />\n<br />\n中共藉腰斬《人民公敵》滅聲<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180926/large/26cf06p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180926%2Flarge%2F26cf06p.jpg&h=9e3a7c87&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n話劇《人民公敵》<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n本月初，德國劇團邵賓納劇院應邀訪華，在北京國家大劇院演出易卜生的話劇《人民公敵》，首演當晚互動環節引發「劇場起義」，觀眾上台高喊言論自由、暗批中共時政，國家大劇院後來要求劇團取消互動環節，該劇後來擬赴南京的演出亦告腰斬。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n觀眾高呼︰為了自由<br />\n<br />\n邵賓納劇院執行總監費特（Tobias Veit）接受媒體採訪時說，在北京國家大劇院演出的結果讓人驚訝，觀眾紛紛向台上演員高喊「因為我們希望有言論自由」、「因為中國的媒體也不講真話」、「因為我們政府一樣不負責任」，持續長達15分鐘。甚至有觀眾說：「這裏也有人被消滅。」<br />\n<br />\n北京首演結束當晚，國家大劇院官員召開緊急會議，與費特討論至凌晨4時半，劇團後來應要求刪除對話環節，但之後的演出仍有觀眾喊出：「為了個人的權利！為了自由！」而網民把事件爆光網上，引起熱議。<br />\n<br />\n其中有觀眾表示：「100年前的這齣戲，我卻看到了今天的中國！」該劇原定9月13及14日在南京江蘇大劇院上演，但從10日開始，劇院網站上就無法購買門票。票務中心表示，是「因舞台技術原因」。<br />\n<br />\n《人民公敵》是挪威劇作家易卜生（Henrik Johan Ibsen）1882年創作的名劇，講述一名醫生發現污染問題，決定將真相公之於世，卻遭弟弟、市政府、記者與出版商的百般阻擾。<br />\n<br />\n德國之聲  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n港人兩度改編　成抗爭名曲<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n瑞典電視台認缺失　華拒收貨<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n港人兩度改編　成抗爭名曲<br />\n<br />\n高唱Do You Hear the People Sing？反中共<br />\n極權滬《孤星淚》觀眾　憑歌「起義」"},{"pid":"24845fdc97a96f2b7e26ad9f9269ca2b94b721e6","tid":836861,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T03:19:25.000Z","msg":"反了 反了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c0ea64fac22caf6596fc56d72b1814bd82bd0e3","tid":836861,"uid":79563,"like":8,"dislike":9,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T03:23:40.000Z","msg":"孤星淚就孤星淚啦屌"},{"pid":"4734910a65ff3cea61b2dc4f87694fba4d41451a","tid":836861,"uid":141151,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"24845fdc97a96f2b7e26ad9f9269ca2b94b721e6","tid":836861,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T03:19:25.000Z","msg":"反了 反了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T03:27:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n邊個用過銀聯支付寶買飛都要搵出黎<br />\n調查所有CCTV微信微博睇下邊個去左現場<br />\n領導公安要親切問候一下"},{"pid":"d96be5e1f1a5cc7a6b3f98a947bb19e75e035474","tid":836861,"uid":141151,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"2c0ea64fac22caf6596fc56d72b1814bd82bd0e3","tid":836861,"uid":79563,"like":8,"dislike":9,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T03:23:40.000Z","msg":"孤星淚就孤星淚啦屌"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T03:29:18.000Z","msg":"《人民公敵》（挪威語：En folkefiende）是挪威劇作家亨利&middot;易卜生於1882年的劇作。易卜生在《人民公敵》之前的一個劇作為1881年的《幽靈》，由於《幽靈》挑戰了維多利亞時代道德觀，於是引起爭議，此外劇中提及梅毒故被公眾視為猥褻，易卜生於是以《人民公敵》回應公眾對《幽靈》的反對聲音。<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c25c22f0e83ebaa56bd98d37745590911b63ae1e","tid":836861,"uid":143499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2c0ea64fac22caf6596fc56d72b1814bd82bd0e3","tid":836861,"uid":79563,"like":8,"dislike":9,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T03:23:40.000Z","msg":"孤星淚就孤星淚啦屌"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T03:42:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffa1064237ed3bd08302063224b69b7670e8c3a6","tid":836861,"uid":47259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c0ea64fac22caf6596fc56d72b1814bd82bd0e3","tid":836861,"uid":79563,"like":8,"dislike":9,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T03:23:40.000Z","msg":"孤星淚就孤星淚啦屌"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T05:26:13.000Z","msg":"下一個一定bam呢齣"},{"pid":"48a6e14c572acf7aa342c4d61b8996f47a94da75","tid":836861,"uid":56999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T05:28:12.000Z","msg":"大陸自己想追求民主自由<br />\n<br />\n但又眼紅香港人有民主自由<br />\n<br />\n正仆街"},{"pid":"1a9b6018166affd7ddacaaf57cc23d6318158a8f","tid":836861,"uid":63154,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T05:29:33.000Z","msg":"過黎香港上演啦，人民公敵真係未睇過"},{"pid":"c49e706fdef0b323890e2d8251c05475d08cecef","tid":836861,"uid":56148,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"48a6e14c572acf7aa342c4d61b8996f47a94da75","tid":836861,"uid":56999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T05:28:12.000Z","msg":"大陸自己想追求民主自由<br />\n<br />\n但又眼紅香港人有民主自由<br />\n<br />\n正仆街"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T05:31:20.000Z","msg":"其實都係魚旦論<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cd0c8f9e5554c40d34083dd0b663e9ecb7ea59b","tid":836861,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T05:32:00.000Z","msg":"支共就係人民公敵<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09caab07989a9e9149263ec3c776196c2ec50fc9","tid":836861,"uid":208159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T05:38:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5ccb1635822e6f4de8886952b23e34339bd56b02","tid":836861,"uid":208159,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T05:39:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d675298d5f951a527e579a9a5de15f3a128fa866","tid":836861,"uid":6799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5cd0c8f9e5554c40d34083dd0b663e9ecb7ea59b","tid":836861,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T05:32:00.000Z","msg":"支共就係人民公敵<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T06:10:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}